{"title":"姑嫂夸车","authors":["揭祥麟"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":8,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑嫂夸车"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揭祥麟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周家院子两姑嫂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂嫂二十妹十八，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当天听过总路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连夜就搞车子化。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑嫂二人学木匠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车子一个造一架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹妹做的鸡公车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂嫂做的三轮卡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹说田坎我能走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂说坡坡我能上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹说我送千担肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂说我推万斤粮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹说我能撵太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳总在我后头亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂说我比风快当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风跑一回我跑几趟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妹说若有上天路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推车去接七仙姑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉皇气得干瞪眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天兵天将追不住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接到我们合作社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"派她去管俱乐部。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫂说若有上天路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推车去会西王母，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要她办个娃娃组，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代替社员当保姆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早送娃娃晚接回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天我好把工做。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑嫂二人把车夸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊醒太阳来观察，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耳听一阵雷声响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车子飞出大院坝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔沙更思插图〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}